msgid "Applied Line Key template \\\"%s\\\" to %d phone(s). Save/Notify is not triggered automatically; use Notify if you want phones to fetch the new config now."
msgstr "已将线路键模板“%s”应用到 %d 部电话。保存/通知不会自动触发；如果您希望手机立即获取新配置，请使用通知。"

msgid "Apply"
msgstr "申请"

msgid "Apply Line Key template \\\"%template%\\\" to %count% selected phone(s)? Existing Line Keys on those phones will be replaced."
msgstr "将线路键模板“%template%”应用于 %count% 部选定的电话？这些电话上现有的线路键将被替换。"

msgid "Apply Line Keys"
msgstr "应用线路键"

msgid "Apply name to tab"
msgstr "将名称应用于选项卡"

msgid "Apply selected template to checked phones"
msgstr "将选定的模板应用到检查的手机"

msgid "Apply template"
msgstr "应用模板"

msgid "Apply to Line Keys"
msgstr "适用于线路键"

msgid "Are you sure you want to delete the selected network(s)?"
msgstr "您确定要删除选定的网络吗？"

msgid "Are you sure you want to delete the selected phone(s)?"
msgstr "您确定要删除选定的电话吗？"

msgid "Assign FreePBX devices to phone lines (Fanvil H2U/H5/H6W/W611W: up to 2 SIP lines)."
msgstr "将 FreePBX 设备分配到电话线路（Fanvil H2U/H5/H6W/W611W：最多 2 条 SIP 线路）。"

msgid "Assign FreePBX devices to phone lines (up to 16 lines supported)"
msgstr "将 FreePBX 设备分配给电话线路（最多支持 16 条线路）"

msgid "Asterisk Manager (AMI) is not available to PHP — SIP NOTIFY was not sent."
msgstr "Asterisk Manager (AMI) 对 PHP 不可用 — SIP NOTIFY 未发送。"

msgid "Asterisk Manager (AMI) is not available to PHP — SIP NOTIFY was not sent. Check Manager access for this admin user."
msgstr "Asterisk Manager (AMI) 对 PHP 不可用 — SIP NOTIFY 未发送。检查此管理员用户的管理员访问权限。"

msgid "Asterisk Manager (AMI) is not available — extra SIP NOTIFY was not sent."
msgstr "Asterisk Manager (AMI) 不可用 — 未发送额外的 SIP NOTIFY。"

msgid "At least one named Line Key template is required."
msgstr "至少需要一个已命名的线路键模板。"

msgid "At least one template is required."
msgstr "至少需要一个模板。"

msgid "Auto"
msgstr "汽车"

msgid "Auto Detect"
msgstr "自动检测"

msgid "Auto or Fanvil for Fanvil H2U/H5/H6W/W611W. Do not choose Yealink for those models - the server would send Yealink text format and the phone will ignore it; Yealink is overridden to Fanvil for H-series models only when this mistake is made."
msgstr "Auto 或 Fanvil 适用于 Fanvil H2U/H5/H6W/W611W。这些型号不要选择 Yealink - 服务器会发送 Yealink 文本格式，手机会忽略它；仅当出现此错误时，Yealink 才会在 H 系列机型上覆盖至 Fanvil。"

msgid "Auto-Provision Repeat Interval (minutes)"
msgstr "自动配置重复间隔（分钟）"

msgid "Auto-Provisioning"
msgstr "自动配置"

msgid "Automatic"
msgstr "自动的"

msgid "Ban after invalid hash attempts"
msgstr "无效哈希尝试后禁止"

msgid "Ban duration (seconds)"
msgstr "禁令持续时间（秒）"

msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

msgid "CIDR must include network and prefix (e.g. 192.168.1.0/24)."
msgstr "CIDR 必须包含网络和前缀（例如 192.168.1.0/24）。"

msgid "CIDR Range"
msgstr "CIDR范围"

msgid "Codec"
msgstr "编解码器"

msgid "Codec Settings"
msgstr "编解码器设置"

msgid "Codecs enabled in FreePBX General SIP Settings (Settings → SIP Settings → Codecs). Set phone priority per codec (0 = disabled on handset, 1–16 = lower number is higher priority). Yealink and Fanvil values are applied during provisioning."
msgstr "在 FreePBX 常规 SIP 设置中启用编解码器（设置 → SIP 设置 → 编解码器）。设置每个编解码器的电话优先级（0 = 在手机上禁用，1–16 = 数字越小优先级越高）。 Yealink 和 Fanvil 值在配置期间应用。"

msgid "Config Version"
msgstr "配置版本"

msgid "Config Version must look like 2.0004 (major.minor, Fanvil Current Config Version)."
msgstr "配置版本必须类似于 2.0004（主要.次要，Fanvil 当前配置版本）。"

msgid "Configure and manage Yealink/Fanvil SIP phones on your FreePBX system."
msgstr "在 FreePBX 系统上配置和管理 Yealink/Fanvil SIP 电话。"

msgid "Configure network-specific settings by IP range (CIDR notation). Settings are applied based on the phone's IP address during provisioning."
msgstr "按 IP 范围（CIDR 表示法）配置网络特定设置。在配置期间根据电话的 IP 地址应用设置。"

msgid "Configure programmable keys for BLF monitoring, speed dial, etc."
msgstr "配置用于 BLF 监控、快速拨号等的可编程按键。"

msgid "Create Line Key Templates in General Settings first."
msgstr "首先在常规设置中创建线路键模板。"

msgid "Create named Line Key templates here for BLF and speed dial layouts. Each tab is a separate template: rename it, configure the keys, then save settings. On Edit Phone, select a template and click Apply to Line Keys to copy it into that phone; the phone is updated only after you save the phone form."
msgstr "在此处为 BLF 和快速拨号布局创建命名的线路键模板。每个选项卡都是一个单独的模板：重命名、配置按键，然后保存设置。在“编辑电话”上，选择一个模板，然后单击“应用到线路键”将其复制到该电话中；仅在保存电话表单后，电话才会更新。"

msgid "Daylight Saving Time"
msgstr "夏令时"

msgid "Dedicated log file (append, one JSON line per event)"
msgstr "专用日志文件（附加，每个事件一行 JSON）"

msgid "Default"
msgstr "默认"

msgid "Default Backlight Timeout (seconds)"
msgstr "默认背光超时（秒）"

msgid "Default display and provisioning behavior for newly discovered phones. Trust certificates controls whether phones accept self-signed HTTPS certificates during provisioning."
msgstr "新发现的电话的默认显示和配置行为。信任证书控制电话在配置期间是否接受自签名 HTTPS 证书。"

msgid "Default Language"
msgstr "默认语言"

msgid "Default Network"
msgstr "默认网络"

msgid "Default NTP, time zone, and daylight-saving values for new phones. Yealink and Fanvil provisioning values are mapped automatically when you save."
msgstr "新手机的默认 NTP、时区和夏令时值。 Yealink 和 Fanvil 配置值会在您保存时自动映射。"

msgid "Default Phone Settings"
msgstr "默认电话设置"

msgid "Default phone web interface users for newly discovered phones. Yealink uses security.user_name.* / security.user_password; Fanvil uses MMI Account settings unless a Network has custom users. The first Administrators row defines the default profile for auto-registered phones."
msgstr "新发现的电话的默认电话 Web 界面用户。亿联使用 security.user_name.* / security.user_password; Fanvil 使用 MMI 帐户设置，除非网络有自定义用户。第一管理员行定义自动注册电话的默认配置文件。"

msgid "Default Time Settings"
msgstr "默认时间设置"

msgid "Defaults used when a new phone is discovered or when an inventory entry has no SIP line bindings yet. Saving these defaults does not overwrite already configured phones."
msgstr "当发现新电话或清单条目尚无 SIP 线路绑定时使用默认值。保存这些默认值不会覆盖已配置的电话。"

msgid "Define up to five Wi-Fi profiles (Networks Edit). Phone Edit selects which SSID to push. Fanvil W611/W611W: Secure Mode 0=None, 1=WPA/WPA2-PSK, 2=802.1x, 3=FT-PSK; Encryption 1=TKIP, 2=AES (CCMP), 3=TKIP+AES."
msgstr "定义最多五个 Wi-Fi 配置文件（网络编辑）。电话编辑选择要推送的 SSID。 Fanvil W611/W611W：安全模式 0=无，1=WPA/WPA2-PSK，2=802.1x，3=FT-PSK；加密 1=TKIP、2=AES (CCMP)、3=TKIP+AES。"

msgid "Delete"
msgstr "删除"

msgid "Delete template"
msgstr "删除模板"

msgid "Delete this template?"
msgstr "删除这个模板吗？"

msgid "Descriptive name; after a line is assigned, saved as {extension}-{Model}-{last 4 MAC chars} (e.g. 6101-T33-A1B2) unless you change it manually. Used as DHCP Hostname in provisioning."
msgstr "描述性名称；分配线路后，保存为 {extension}-{Model}-{last 4 MAC chars}（例如 6101-T33-A1B2），除非您手动更改。在配置中用作 DHCP 主机名。"

msgid "Device name is required."
msgstr "设备名称为必填项。"

msgid "DHCP setup: publish this URL to phones as their provisioning server, usually with DHCP Option 66 (or the vendor-specific provisioning URL option used in your phone VLAN). Phones should receive this URL and then request their MAC-based config from ZeroTouchSIP."
msgstr "DHCP 设置：将此 URL 发布到电话作为其配置服务器，通常使用 DHCP 选项 66（或电话 VLAN 中使用的供应商特定的配置 URL 选项）。电话应接收此 URL，然后从 ZeroTouchSIP 请求基于 MAC 的配置。"

